00:01:31,500 --> 00:01:35,300
= Princess Agents =

15
00:01:35,340 --> 00:01:37,940
= Episode 29 =

16
00:01:45,520 --> 00:01:46,630
Wei Shuyou!

17
00:01:53,040 --> 00:01:54,380
You bastard!

18
00:01:54,380 --> 00:01:56,010
How dare you call my name!

19
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:59,030
Surrender now

20
00:01:59,360 --> 00:02:01,600
to die intact.

21
00:04:54,980 --> 00:04:57,930
I killed those men and hurt him.

22
00:05:07,320 --> 00:05:09,150
Do your job.

23
00:05:14,260 --> 00:05:15,010
If we don’t take action now,

24
00:05:15,010 --> 00:05:16,520
it’ll be too late to save His Excellency.

25
00:05:17,190 --> 00:05:18,460
Anything we do

26
00:05:18,460 --> 00:05:20,000
will prove Yan Xun guilty.

27
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:21,790
We can’t leap in the dark anymore.

28
00:05:23,660 --> 00:05:25,100
But Emperor is fickle

29
00:05:25,100 --> 00:05:26,450
and gullible.

30
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:29,300
At court, His Excellency will...

31
00:05:35,730 --> 00:05:36,590
I have an idea.

32
00:05:41,350 --> 00:05:42,490
It’s feasible.

33
00:05:43,260 --> 00:05:44,500
But you’ll be in grave danger.

34
00:05:44,500 --> 00:05:45,530
I’ll do it.

35
00:05:46,490 --> 00:05:47,910
Alright, I can’t go see her.

36
00:05:47,910 --> 00:05:48,890
Only you can.

37
00:05:52,260 --> 00:05:53,120
Time is running out.

38
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:53,730
Any delay,

39
00:05:53,730 --> 00:05:54,570
we’ll be stuck in here.

40
00:05:55,860 --> 00:05:57,890
Fine, you take care.

41
00:06:06,510 --> 00:06:07,310
Princess.

42
00:06:08,320 --> 00:06:09,250
What’s wrong?

43
00:06:09,250 --> 00:06:10,340
His Excellency Yan Xun’s maid

44
00:06:10,340 --> 00:06:11,520
bought over an entrance guard,

45
00:06:11,520 --> 00:06:12,720
and is waiting outside.

46
00:06:13,200 --> 00:06:15,380
She says that His Excellency Yan Xun is in trouble

47
00:06:15,380 --> 00:06:16,580
and needs your help.

48
00:06:21,440 --> 00:06:22,110
Move!

49
00:06:25,870 --> 00:06:26,730
Mr. Zhu,

50
00:06:27,340 --> 00:06:28,640
Young Master Wei Shuyou failed.

51
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:30,100
Yan Xun is being sent to the Palace

52
00:06:30,100 --> 00:06:30,830
to see His Majesty.

53
00:06:30,830 --> 00:06:31,510
Young Master asked us

54
00:06:31,510 --> 00:06:32,550
to move the killers’ bodies away

55
00:06:32,550 --> 00:06:34,090
on the sly.

56
00:06:36,860 --> 00:06:37,590
Go check.

57
00:06:37,590 --> 00:06:38,280
Aye.

58
00:06:40,350 --> 00:06:42,320
You guys take the chance

59
00:06:42,320 --> 00:06:44,270
to bury those bodies.

60
00:06:44,270 --> 00:06:45,030
Be quick.

61
00:06:45,030 --> 00:06:45,980
- Aye.
- Aye.

62
00:06:55,220 --> 00:06:56,230
Take those bodies away.

63
00:07:39,290 --> 00:07:39,950
Get lost!

64
00:07:46,900 --> 00:07:47,900
Princess has orders

65
00:07:47,900 --> 00:07:49,630
to secure the killers’ bodies.

66
00:07:49,630 --> 00:07:50,250
Go!

67
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:51,630
Move!

68
00:08:01,270 --> 00:08:02,040
Mr. Zhu,

69
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:03,980
someone ambushed Wei’s guards.

70
00:08:03,980 --> 00:08:05,110
Those bodies were taken away

71
00:08:05,110 --> 00:08:06,080
by Princess’s men.

72
00:08:07,370 --> 00:08:08,810
That useless Wei Shuyou!

73
00:08:08,810 --> 00:08:10,500
Mr. Zhu, what’s next?

74
00:08:10,500 --> 00:08:12,330
You need to ask? Get them back!

75
00:08:12,330 --> 00:08:13,150
- Aye.
- Let’s go!

76
00:08:28,460 --> 00:08:31,030
Take them outside the city.

77
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,360
They’ll be unconscious there

78
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,860
for at least for 4 hours.

79
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:36,130
They won’t make any trouble.

80
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:38,470
Your Majesty, your liquor pot is empty.

81
00:09:38,470 --> 00:09:40,510
Here’s more.

82
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:47,520
Who are you?

83
00:09:49,210 --> 00:09:50,590
I’m your maid

84
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:51,970
and your woman.

85
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:56,210
My woman?

86
00:09:58,740 --> 00:10:01,350
Everyone and everything in this world

87
00:10:01,680 --> 00:10:03,400
belong to you.

88
00:10:07,090 --> 00:10:08,800
Aren’t you sweet?

89
00:10:23,380 --> 00:10:24,590
What’s your name?

90
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:28,760
My name is Lan’er.

91
00:10:50,140 --> 00:10:51,340
Lan’er.

92
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:10,020
Your Majesty!

93
00:11:10,290 --> 00:11:11,740
Your Majesty. Are you asleep?

94
00:11:12,410 --> 00:11:13,920
It’s urgent!

95
00:11:14,490 --> 00:11:16,450
Your Majesty! Your Majesty!

96
00:11:27,170 --> 00:11:28,180
Come in.

97
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:34,910
Your Majesty.

98
00:11:35,990 --> 00:11:37,230
What happened?

99
00:11:37,470 --> 00:11:38,610
Something urgent

100
00:11:38,610 --> 00:11:39,970
requires your immediate attention.

101
00:11:55,790 --> 00:11:59,630
She is good. Promote her to Concubine

102
00:11:59,740 --> 00:12:00,960
with the title Lan.

103
00:12:01,800 --> 00:12:03,570
She can move into the Palace of Orchid.

104
00:12:04,790 --> 00:12:05,510
Aye.

105
00:12:10,590 --> 00:12:13,970
Yan Xun, I’ve just pardoned you.

106
00:12:14,330 --> 00:12:15,940
You haven’t atoned for your sins

107
00:12:16,190 --> 00:12:18,010
before wounding others.

108
00:12:19,920 --> 00:12:21,110
I’m guilty.

109
00:12:21,380 --> 00:12:24,050
I can’t thank you enough
for your kindness.

110
00:12:25,050 --> 00:12:27,900
But that was self-defense.

111
00:12:28,570 --> 00:12:30,140
Wei Shuyou attempted
to assassinate me earlier.

112
00:12:30,140 --> 00:12:31,380
If I didn’t fight back,

113
00:12:31,380 --> 00:12:32,720
I wouldn’t have a chance to survive.

114
00:12:32,930 --> 00:12:34,660
Your Majesty,

115
00:12:35,160 --> 00:12:36,570
I went there

116
00:12:36,570 --> 00:12:37,740
for Yan Xun’s safety

117
00:12:37,740 --> 00:12:38,980
to patrol as usual.

118
00:12:39,250 --> 00:12:41,250
But I caught him

119
00:12:42,140 --> 00:12:43,400
trying to escape,

120
00:12:43,810 --> 00:12:45,420
so he wanted me dead.

121
00:12:45,860 --> 00:12:46,830
Your Majesty.

122
00:12:46,830 --> 00:12:48,850
Just like his father,

123
00:12:49,050 --> 00:12:52,710
Yan Xun is too wild to be trusted.

124
00:12:52,710 --> 00:12:54,670
Are you blind?

125
00:12:55,100 --> 00:12:55,850
Can’t you see

126
00:12:55,850 --> 00:12:56,780
those dead bodies

127
00:12:56,780 --> 00:12:57,690
all over the Oriole Courtyard?

128
00:12:58,200 --> 00:13:00,220
Wei Shuyou assembled the assassins

129
00:13:00,370 --> 00:13:01,340
and Yan Xun

130
00:13:01,340 --> 00:13:02,460
just tried to protect himself.

131
00:13:02,460 --> 00:13:03,670
Prince Yu.

132
00:13:03,670 --> 00:13:04,860
Don’t you believe

133
00:13:04,860 --> 00:13:05,420
your own cousin?

134
00:13:05,420 --> 00:13:07,120
Did you see any assassins, Your Highness?

135
00:13:07,500 --> 00:13:09,150
Or did you see any dead bodies?

136
00:13:12,540 --> 00:13:13,690
I didn’t.

137
00:13:13,910 --> 00:13:15,090
- But...
- Song.

138
00:13:16,750 --> 00:13:17,560
Stand down.

139
00:13:19,570 --> 00:13:21,460
Your Majesty, I have got the testimonies

140
00:13:21,460 --> 00:13:23,700
from the guards overnight.

141
00:13:23,950 --> 00:13:26,460
They only saw Wei Shuyou and Yan Xun

142
00:13:26,460 --> 00:13:27,790
without any sign of assassins.

143
00:13:55,930 --> 00:13:59,530
Your Majesty,
guards of the Oriole Courtyard

144
00:13:59,530 --> 00:14:01,070
all came from the Yuwen family.

145
00:14:01,320 --> 00:14:03,870
Their testimonies are unreliable.

146
00:14:04,550 --> 00:14:06,920
Your Majesty, I understand

147
00:14:07,030 --> 00:14:09,670
it’s hard for me to defend myself.

148
00:14:10,420 --> 00:14:13,730
But I grew up in the capital city.

149
00:14:14,060 --> 00:14:15,610
Your Majesty are
a good judge of character.

150
00:14:15,980 --> 00:14:17,170
What kind of person am I?

151
00:14:17,550 --> 00:14:19,210
Would I stoop so low

152
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:21,330
as to act as the crooked?

153
00:14:22,830 --> 00:14:23,970
I believe

154
00:14:24,420 --> 00:14:26,130
Your Majesty will have
your own conclusions.

155
00:14:29,660 --> 00:14:32,510
Your Majesty,
if you punish Yan Xun for this,

156
00:14:32,780 --> 00:14:34,450
that may be categorized as persecution.

157
00:14:37,840 --> 00:14:40,070
Like father like son.

158
00:14:40,810 --> 00:14:42,950
Here you are playing the martyr.

159
00:14:43,710 --> 00:14:45,370
You not only framed Young Master Wei,

160
00:14:45,370 --> 00:14:47,430
but also fooled Noble Consort.

161
00:14:48,480 --> 00:14:49,250
You are much better

162
00:14:49,250 --> 00:14:50,980
than that treacherous father

163
00:14:50,980 --> 00:14:53,250
of yours.

164
00:14:54,240 --> 00:14:55,640
What’s this called?

165
00:14:56,370 --> 00:14:58,910
The son outdoes the father.

166
00:15:04,500 --> 00:15:05,520
Young Master Huai.

167
00:15:06,940 --> 00:15:08,880
If I were really as good as you said,

168
00:15:09,830 --> 00:15:10,840
I wouldn’t have

169
00:15:10,840 --> 00:15:12,040
ended up like this.

170
00:15:13,180 --> 00:15:16,210
But thanks for showing me a backstabber,

171
00:15:16,400 --> 00:15:19,100
fabricator and liar.

172
00:15:20,830 --> 00:15:22,270
I’ve learned

173
00:15:22,880 --> 00:15:24,250
my lesson.

174
00:15:25,110 --> 00:15:26,230
Your Excellency,

175
00:15:26,230 --> 00:15:27,970
don’t throw dirt on me.

176
00:15:27,970 --> 00:15:30,120
His Majesty can tell the truth.

177
00:15:30,300 --> 00:15:31,450
Well,

178
00:15:32,790 --> 00:15:34,360
you wounded others

179
00:15:34,950 --> 00:15:36,260
in custody.

180
00:15:36,260 --> 00:15:37,700
We all saw that.

181
00:15:38,330 --> 00:15:41,740
Who saw your so-called assassins?

182
00:15:42,530 --> 00:15:43,770
Do you have eyewitnesses?

183
00:15:43,980 --> 00:15:46,300
You are lying to His Majesty.

184
00:15:50,420 --> 00:15:53,500
He who has a mind to beat his dog
will easily find his stick.

185
00:15:56,230 --> 00:15:58,890
I’m only a concubine’s son
with no power at all.

186
00:15:59,860 --> 00:16:01,760
Telling lies aside,

187
00:16:01,760 --> 00:16:04,130
I wouldn’t dare to wound anyone.

188
00:16:06,250 --> 00:16:07,680
You overestimated me.

189
00:16:11,940 --> 00:16:12,910
Yuwen Huai.

190
00:16:13,290 --> 00:16:14,830
You alone aren’t that capable, of course.

191
00:16:20,920 --> 00:16:22,640
My respects to you, Father, Mother.

192
00:16:23,090 --> 00:16:24,240
What are you doing here?

193
00:16:24,790 --> 00:16:25,630
Don’t mess around.

194
00:16:25,630 --> 00:16:26,610
Go back, now.

195
00:16:27,290 --> 00:16:28,210
Father,

196
00:16:28,210 --> 00:16:29,090
I’ve got something important

197
00:16:29,090 --> 00:16:29,910
to report.

198
00:16:30,740 --> 00:16:31,440
Go ahead.

199
00:16:32,230 --> 00:16:33,590
The dead body outside

200
00:16:33,590 --> 00:16:35,010
was the assassin

201
00:16:35,010 --> 00:16:36,280
sent by the Wei family

202
00:16:36,280 --> 00:16:37,140
to kill Yan Xun tonight,

203
00:16:37,140 --> 00:16:38,640
and he was

204
00:16:38,640 --> 00:16:39,830
Wei Shuyou’s henchman.

205
00:16:40,250 --> 00:16:41,590
Wei Shuyou always went out

206
00:16:41,590 --> 00:16:42,580
with him.

207
00:16:42,770 --> 00:16:44,530
Many people in the Palace recognize him.

208
00:16:45,070 --> 00:16:46,530
And some of you here

209
00:16:46,890 --> 00:16:47,770
must be familiar with him

210
00:16:47,770 --> 00:16:48,980
as well.

211
00:16:49,630 --> 00:16:52,120
Young Master Yuwen, am I right?

212
00:16:57,340 --> 00:16:59,580
Song, Yuwen Huai,

213
00:16:59,710 --> 00:17:00,880
check the body outside.

214
00:17:02,790 --> 00:17:03,850
- Aye.
- Aye.

215
00:17:24,390 --> 00:17:25,160
Your Majesty.

216
00:17:26,460 --> 00:17:28,750
The dead man was indeed

217
00:17:28,750 --> 00:17:29,960
Wei Shuyou’s henchman.

218
00:17:29,960 --> 00:17:31,500
What Chun just said is true.

219
00:17:35,260 --> 00:17:37,320
Young Master Yuwen, don’t you

220
00:17:37,320 --> 00:17:38,800
recognize him?

221
00:17:42,880 --> 00:17:46,030
He looked familiar, but I don’t know him.

222
00:17:47,380 --> 00:17:48,350
Yuwen Huai.

223
00:17:48,560 --> 00:17:50,390
What do you mean by “he looked familiar”?

224
00:17:50,390 --> 00:17:51,250
You hang about

225
00:17:51,250 --> 00:17:52,230
with Wei Shuyou every day.

226
00:17:52,230 --> 00:17:53,090
How could you not know

227
00:17:53,090 --> 00:17:54,160
his henchman?

228
00:17:54,780 --> 00:17:57,500
Shuyou, go and check the body,

229
00:17:58,100 --> 00:17:59,810
and see if he was

230
00:17:59,810 --> 00:18:00,630
your servant.

231
00:18:01,320 --> 00:18:02,760
Look carefully.

232
00:18:03,420 --> 00:18:04,820
Don’t you think

233
00:18:05,170 --> 00:18:06,600
you can muddle through this

234
00:18:06,600 --> 00:18:08,370
by telling lies.

235
00:18:09,180 --> 00:18:10,230
You know,

236
00:18:10,230 --> 00:18:11,550
I have got so many ways

237
00:18:11,550 --> 00:18:13,520
to verify your story.

238
00:18:14,790 --> 00:18:15,590
Aye.

239
00:18:39,360 --> 00:18:41,640
Your Majesty. Your Highnesses.

240
00:18:42,180 --> 00:18:44,160
It’s true that man

241
00:18:44,160 --> 00:18:44,920
was my servant.

242
00:18:46,430 --> 00:18:48,710
Did you hear that, Yuwen Huai?

243
00:18:48,850 --> 00:18:50,590
He has admitted it himself.

244
00:18:50,590 --> 00:18:52,030
What more do you have to say?

245
00:18:53,020 --> 00:18:56,340
Your Highness,
although he was their servant,

246
00:18:56,860 --> 00:18:58,700
he could be a spy

247
00:18:58,700 --> 00:19:00,880
planted next to Young Master Wei.

248
00:19:02,160 --> 00:19:02,500
You...

249
00:19:02,500 --> 00:19:03,630
By the way,

250
00:19:05,820 --> 00:19:07,620
when Marquis Dingbei planned to

251
00:19:07,620 --> 00:19:08,380
rebel,

252
00:19:09,020 --> 00:19:11,500
he could certainly plant spies

253
00:19:11,500 --> 00:19:12,570
in noble families.

254
00:19:13,020 --> 00:19:13,690
You...

255
00:19:14,380 --> 00:19:15,170
That’s right.

256
00:19:15,610 --> 00:19:16,880
How could Princess know

257
00:19:16,880 --> 00:19:17,910
what happened in the Oriole Courtyard

258
00:19:17,910 --> 00:19:19,510
in the middle of the night,

259
00:19:19,960 --> 00:19:22,010
and then encountered the assassin

260
00:19:22,010 --> 00:19:23,600
and brought him to His Majesty?

261
00:19:24,390 --> 00:19:25,260
Your Majesty.

262
00:19:25,770 --> 00:19:27,640
This man was my servant,

263
00:19:27,640 --> 00:19:29,170
but never a henchman.

264
00:19:29,370 --> 00:19:30,840
He seemed to be smart,

265
00:19:30,840 --> 00:19:32,310
so I kept him.

266
00:19:32,310 --> 00:19:33,070
I didn’t expect

267
00:19:33,070 --> 00:19:34,330
he was skilled in martial arts.

268
00:19:35,060 --> 00:19:37,480
I bet someone powerful

269
00:19:37,480 --> 00:19:39,340
planted him next to me.

270
00:19:42,880 --> 00:19:44,890
I have been living in the capital
since childhood.

271
00:19:45,250 --> 00:19:46,620
I have always been cautious

272
00:19:47,370 --> 00:19:49,080
to stay away from mistakes

273
00:19:49,080 --> 00:19:50,300
and trouble.

274
00:19:51,040 --> 00:19:52,690
I don’t have

275
00:19:53,160 --> 00:19:54,940
any fighters around me,

276
00:19:54,940 --> 00:19:55,800
not to mention highly skilled ones.

277
00:19:55,800 --> 00:19:56,970
Liar!

278
00:19:57,230 --> 00:19:58,350
There are two

279
00:19:58,350 --> 00:19:59,580
skilled martial artists around you.

280
00:19:59,580 --> 00:20:00,840
A man and a woman.

281
00:20:01,170 --> 00:20:02,630
Your Majesty,
if you have no idea about that,

282
00:20:02,760 --> 00:20:04,730
we can bring them here for questioning.

283
00:20:05,150 --> 00:20:06,280
Your Majesty, the truth is

284
00:20:07,350 --> 00:20:09,390
Wei Shuyou planned
to assassinate me first.

285
00:20:09,560 --> 00:20:11,030
And now, he’s framing me.

286
00:20:11,730 --> 00:20:14,280
He’s evil beyond forgiveness.

287
00:20:14,680 --> 00:20:16,440
