581
00:37:04,810 --> 00:37:06,530
in Qingshan House.

582
00:37:06,530 --> 00:37:07,720
Are you threatening me?

583
00:37:07,920 --> 00:37:09,800
What do you think?

584
00:37:10,390 --> 00:37:13,080
You may be fine

585
00:37:13,080 --> 00:37:14,460
with being laughed at

586
00:37:14,460 --> 00:37:16,450
for the internal strife.

587
00:37:17,210 --> 00:37:18,580
But aren’t you afraid

588
00:37:18,580 --> 00:37:19,840
your grandmother’s reappearance

589
00:37:20,250 --> 00:37:21,910
will destroy

590
00:37:21,910 --> 00:37:23,460
the entire Third Branch?

591
00:37:26,830 --> 00:37:28,840
Once the secret is revealed,

592
00:37:29,910 --> 00:37:32,220
I may not get away with it.

593
00:37:34,030 --> 00:37:36,000
But you are also a Yuwen.

594
00:37:36,490 --> 00:37:38,150
You can’t

595
00:37:39,230 --> 00:37:40,520
stay out of it, either.

596
00:37:41,100 --> 00:37:43,390
Fine. We’ll see.

597
00:37:45,220 --> 00:37:47,070
If I told His Majesty

598
00:37:47,310 --> 00:37:48,940
about your branch

599
00:37:48,940 --> 00:37:50,290
colluding with the spies from Liang,

600
00:37:51,440 --> 00:37:53,620
would he

601
00:37:53,620 --> 00:37:55,310
let me off the hook

602
00:37:55,620 --> 00:37:57,020
for telling the truth?

603
00:37:58,310 --> 00:37:59,560
Yuwen Yue.

604
00:38:01,250 --> 00:38:03,030
What the hell do you want?

605
00:38:03,030 --> 00:38:05,420
I’m about to go to the border.

606
00:38:06,360 --> 00:38:09,000
Wild wind, bad weather.

607
00:38:09,300 --> 00:38:10,630
Not comfortable to live there.

608
00:38:12,230 --> 00:38:14,890
While I am there suffering,

609
00:38:15,490 --> 00:38:16,350
you can still

610
00:38:16,910 --> 00:38:18,950
enjoy yourself in your mansion.

611
00:38:19,790 --> 00:38:22,570
I don’t have a big heart. It upsets me.

612
00:38:23,530 --> 00:38:24,160
How about this?

613
00:38:25,600 --> 00:38:27,240
I have another place for you to stay.

614
00:38:29,020 --> 00:38:30,260
Go guard the Imperial Mausoleum.

615
00:38:31,570 --> 00:38:33,100
Because you are really good at

616
00:38:33,100 --> 00:38:34,690
dealing with dead people.

617
00:38:35,920 --> 00:38:37,800
I give you three days
to volunteer for the job.

618
00:38:38,620 --> 00:38:39,910
I don’t want to see you in the city

619
00:38:40,570 --> 00:38:42,200
before I leave.

620
00:38:42,960 --> 00:38:44,170
Or,

621
00:38:44,500 --> 00:38:45,530
I’ll send you to hell

622
00:38:46,030 --> 00:38:47,690
to accompany your grandfather.

623
00:38:48,520 --> 00:38:49,760
Yuwen Yue,

624
00:38:51,380 --> 00:38:53,700
how dare you!

625
00:39:15,880 --> 00:39:16,770
Young Master.

626
00:39:18,380 --> 00:39:19,110
Young Master.

627
00:39:20,630 --> 00:39:21,760
Come in.

628
00:39:25,830 --> 00:39:27,530
Young Master, good news.

629
00:39:27,820 --> 00:39:29,500
Yuwen Yue is leaving Chang’an

630
00:39:29,500 --> 00:39:30,360
for the border

631
00:39:30,360 --> 00:39:31,330
tomorrow morning.

632
00:39:41,550 --> 00:39:42,750
Young… Young Master…

633
00:39:42,750 --> 00:39:44,700
Why are you hitting me?

634
00:39:45,170 --> 00:39:46,730
No reason.

635
00:39:47,430 --> 00:39:49,190
You deserve it.

636
00:40:16,660 --> 00:40:17,410
Your Highness.

637
00:40:24,550 --> 00:40:27,130
I received a secret report.

638
00:40:27,920 --> 00:40:29,630
Yuwen Xi’s wife

639
00:40:29,760 --> 00:40:31,220
has been moved to Qingshan House

640
00:40:31,220 --> 00:40:32,660
from the Pleasure Pavilion.

641
00:40:37,640 --> 00:40:39,300
No wonder Yuwen Huai

642
00:40:39,300 --> 00:40:40,220
volunteered

643
00:40:40,220 --> 00:40:41,780
to guard the Imperial Mausoleum.

644
00:40:43,240 --> 00:40:47,010
Yuwen Yue must’ve had

645
00:40:48,770 --> 00:40:50,880
dirt on him.

646
00:40:50,880 --> 00:40:52,570
You are really wise.

647
00:41:11,000 --> 00:41:13,130
Your Excellency, as per His Majesty’s order,

648
00:41:13,130 --> 00:41:14,660
we’ll be guarding this courtyard.

649
00:41:17,090 --> 00:41:18,810
And Prince Yu asked me

650
00:41:18,810 --> 00:41:20,380
to bring you this sword

651
00:41:20,560 --> 00:41:22,150
to return it to its original owner.

652
00:41:29,570 --> 00:41:32,120
Please extend my gratitude to him.

653
00:41:32,760 --> 00:41:33,360
Aye.

654
00:41:33,810 --> 00:41:34,920
Starting from tomorrow,

655
00:41:34,920 --> 00:41:36,300
the lockdown will be lifted.

656
00:41:36,630 --> 00:41:37,840
Except for His Excellency,

657
00:41:37,840 --> 00:41:39,410
everyone has free access to the courtyard.

658
00:41:49,070 --> 00:41:51,310
Your Excellency, it’s true

659
00:41:51,310 --> 00:41:52,590
that Yuwen Huai and Yuwen Yue

660
00:41:52,590 --> 00:41:54,220
will leave the city.

661
00:41:54,830 --> 00:41:56,690
The Yuwen family won’t target us for now.

662
00:41:57,070 --> 00:41:58,260
Although our biggest enemy Yuwen Huai

663
00:41:58,260 --> 00:41:59,550
is gone,

664
00:42:00,300 --> 00:42:02,110
we still need to be cautious.

665
00:42:02,760 --> 00:42:03,830
I understand.

666
00:42:09,730 --> 00:42:10,650
Taste the dishes

667
00:42:10,650 --> 00:42:11,670
from my hometown.

668
00:42:11,940 --> 00:42:13,330
Haven’t had these for a while.

669
00:42:14,390 --> 00:42:15,220
Have they been tested?

670
00:42:15,220 --> 00:42:16,050
Your Excellency.

671
00:42:17,300 --> 00:42:19,060
Your Excellency, Ajing is here.

672
00:42:20,440 --> 00:42:22,880
Ajing, do you remember me?

673
00:42:24,840 --> 00:42:27,690
Your Excellency, I thought

674
00:42:27,690 --> 00:42:29,630
I’d never see you again.

675
00:42:31,490 --> 00:42:32,380
Get up.

676
00:42:32,860 --> 00:42:34,020
Where is General Meng He?

677
00:42:38,960 --> 00:42:39,930
Your Excellency.

678
00:42:40,830 --> 00:42:43,750
My father died on the battlefield.

679
00:42:44,020 --> 00:42:44,950
His last words were

680
00:42:45,110 --> 00:42:47,120
to find you.

681
00:42:47,320 --> 00:42:48,230
Luckily,

682
00:42:48,970 --> 00:42:50,740
I survived the war.

683
00:42:51,580 --> 00:42:52,930
Then I came to Chang’an.

684
00:42:53,380 --> 00:42:54,990
I looked for you for three months

685
00:42:55,180 --> 00:42:57,410
before finally meeting Zhong Yu.

686
00:42:58,310 --> 00:43:02,410
Your Excellency, my father died a tragic death.

687
00:43:03,440 --> 00:43:04,510
Rest assured.

688
00:43:06,080 --> 00:43:07,900
We will take revenge for the deceased.

689
00:43:08,930 --> 00:43:12,340
Your Excellency, I want to follow you around.

690
00:43:12,660 --> 00:43:14,340
I can cook

691
00:43:14,450 --> 00:43:15,650
and wrestle.

692
00:43:15,650 --> 00:43:17,460
I will do whatever

693
00:43:17,460 --> 00:43:18,640
I can for you.

694
00:43:19,310 --> 00:43:20,050
Good.

695
00:43:20,920 --> 00:43:22,470
You can be my guard.

696
00:43:22,980 --> 00:43:24,210
Thank you, Your Excellency.

